  "response": "\"Death Note II: The Last Name\" is a Japanese live-action film based on the popular manga and anime series \"Death Note.\" If you're looking to watch it dubbed in English, here are some options that you might consider:\n\n1. **Streaming Services**: Platforms like Netflix, Hulu, and Amazon Prime Video sometimes offer dubbed versions of popular international films. Check if they have \"Death Note II: The Last Name\" available in their library.\n\n2. **DVD/Blu-ray**: Physical copies of the movie might be available for purchase on websites like Amazon, eBay, or specialty online stores that focus on anime and manga. These often include dubbed versions.\n\n3. **Anime-Specific Platforms**: Services such as Crunchyroll, Funimation, and VRV often have a wide range of dubbed content. Check their catalogs to see if they offer this particular movie.\n\n4. **Local Libraries or Rental Services**: Some libraries and rental services might have a copy of the movie available for borrowing.\n\nRemember to verify the availability of the dubbed version specifically, as some platforms might only offer the subtitled version.",
